pairing.definition: Δ_n,Δ_p are 3-point OES on B_obs (AME2020): Δ_n=|(-1)^N (B(N+1)-2B(N)+B(N-1))/2|, Δ_p analogous in Z.
pairing.radius_correction: r -> r + k_n*Δ_n + k_p*Δ_p (k_n,k_p frozen by weighted LS on non-magic centers)

fit_protocol.train_centers: exclude centers at observed magic numbers (axis-specific)
